          "text": "Something you notice when switching tools is that some tools are incredibly reliable and others are immensely functional.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "It’s rare to find a tool that does both.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Classic example:",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Wrike",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "isn’t functional—it’s pretty outdated—but it",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "is",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "reliable. If I click on ‘time tracking,’ for example, it shows me what’s tracked every time.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.wrike.com/main/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Clickup",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "is radically functional. There are dozens of features and helpful things you can do. But for all its hype, it’s hardly reliable—whether it shows me what it’s",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "suppose",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "to show me in a certain space or dashboard is often hit or miss.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://clickup.com/"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Airtable",
          "marks": [
            "link-0"
          ]
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "is rare indeed. It’s both reliable—in that it does what I expect it to,",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "every time",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "—and functional—in that it offers specific features for specific tasks (and allows users’ to customize them to their liking).",
          "marks": []
        }
      ],
      "markDefs": [
        {
          "_key": "link-0",
          "_type": "link",
          "href": "https://www.airtable.com/"
